# Nakili faili hii → .env.local (haijafuatiliwa na Git).
#
# === Production / Preview (lazima) ===
# Vercel: Project → Settings → Environment Variables (Production + Preview)
# GitHub Actions: Repository → Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions
#   - VITE_SUPABASE_URL      (mf. https://xxxx.supabase.co)
#   - VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY (anon / publishable — SI service_role)
# Ikiwa Secrets hazijawekwa, CI hutumia fallback salama (kmktciunit.supabase.co) kwa build tu.
#
# Gharama: Supabase (free tier) + Vercel (free/hobby). Sentry ni hiari.

# Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_publishable_or_anon_key_here
#
# STORAGE: Buckets zinaweza kuonekana "Unknown" au "Needs Setup" kwenye System Health
# ikiwa URL/ANON_KEY zinaelekeza mradi tofauti wa Supabase kuliko ule ulio na migrations.
# Hakikisha Vercel/GitHub Secrets zinaelekeza mradi mmoja, kisha: npm run db:push:safe
# Realtime (websocket): chaguomsingi ni true (build bila hii = washwa). Weka false ikiwa mtandao unazuia WebSocket.
# Supabase Dashboard → Database → Publications: jedwali kwenye supabase_realtime (tazama migrations za portal).
VITE_SUPABASE_REALTIME_ENABLED=true

# Hiari: kanoni na og:url wakati wa build (mfano https://portal.example.com — bila slash ya mwisho)
# VITE_PUBLIC_SITE_ORIGIN=

# Hiari: ufuatiliaji wa makosa (weka DSN ya mradi wa Browser kwenye sentry.io; paketi: npm i @sentry/react)
# VITE_SENTRY_DSN=

# AI Assistant (frontend switch tu; hakuna siri hapa)
# AI requests zitapitia Supabase Edge Function (server side)
VITE_AI_ASSISTANT_ENABLED=false
VITE_AI_FUNCTION_NAME=portal-ai-assistant
